        %li
          Examples
          %p
            Check here
            %input{:name => "exbline", :type => "checkbox", :value => "X"}/
            if
            you would like to see the words used for indexing each Japanese example sentence.
            %br/
            %font{:size => "-1"}
              (This is rather technical stuff, mainly used by people
              maintaining the Examples file.)
        %li
          preset your name and email address if you are sending in new
          entries, amendments, comments on example sentences, etc.
          %ul
            %li
              name:
              %input{:name => "exuname", :size => "40", :type => "text", :value => "Name"}/
            %li
              email address:
              %input{:name => "exemail", :size => "60", :type => "text", :value => "Email address"}/
          Note that for obscure technical reasons, neither the name nor the email
          address can contain an underscore ("_").
      %input{:type => "submit", :value => "Customize"}/
